{"word":"G5574 - ψεύδομαι - pseúdomai - psyoo'-dom-ahee - Falsely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψεύδομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pseúdomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">psyoo'-dom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Falsely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொய் சொல், பொய்யுரை"},{"paragraph":"to lie, to speak deliberate falsehoods"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice of an apparently primary verb; to <i>utter an untruth</i> or attempt to <i>deceive</i> by falsehood: - falsely, lie.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5571/5571\">G5571</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572/5572\">G5572</a>, <a href=\"#/G5573/5573\">G5573</a>, <a href=\"#/G5574/5574\">G5574</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575/5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576/5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577/5577\">G5577</a>, <a href=\"#/G5578/5578\">G5578</a>, <a href=\"#/G5579/5579\">G5579</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580/5580\">G5580</a>, <a href=\"#/G5581/5581\">G5581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5582/5582\">G5582</a>, <a href=\"#/G5583/5583\">G5583</a>, <a href=\"#/G893/893\">G893</a>"}]}